00:00:03.620 --> 00:00:07.130
How to Turn Your House into a Winter Wonderland.

00:00:07.130 --> 00:00:13.400
Frolic and play -- indoors -- the Eskimo way
by turning your home into a winter wonderland.

00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:21.340
You will need Christmas tree Cans of spray
snow Clear Christmas lights White, glass,

00:00:21.340 --> 00:00:30.279
and silver ornaments Various winter decorations
Silver bells Pine cones Silver or white candles

00:00:30.279 --> 00:00:39.380
Candle holders Crystal frost Snowflake gossamer
Empty boxes White wrapping paper and ribbon.

00:00:39.380 --> 00:00:40.559
Step 1.

00:00:40.559 --> 00:00:44.579
Spray a Christmas tree with fake snow, and
string clear lights around it.

00:00:44.579 --> 00:00:49.239
Decorate the tree with white, glass, and silver
ornaments, icicles, and snowflakes.

00:00:49.239 --> 00:00:52.940
Add garlands of white, silver, or pale blue
ribbon.

00:00:52.940 --> 00:00:53.970
Step 2.

00:00:53.970 --> 00:00:59.090
Bring the tree to life by putting decorative
red berries, birds, and bird nests in the

00:00:59.090 --> 00:01:00.090
branches.

00:01:00.090 --> 00:01:04.220
Add additional Christmas trees around your
house to make an enchanted forest.

00:01:04.220 --> 00:01:05.220
Step 3.

00:01:05.220 --> 00:01:09.801
Lay a white tablecloth across your table,
and add small decorations like doves, silver

00:01:09.801 --> 00:01:11.570
bells, or pine cones.

00:01:11.570 --> 00:01:15.830
Add light with white or silver candles in
candle holders, and spray the holders with

00:01:15.830 --> 00:01:16.830
crystal frost.

00:01:16.830 --> 00:01:21.570
Invest in a nice centerpiece for the table
that can be used year after year.

00:01:21.570 --> 00:01:22.690
Step 4.

00:01:22.690 --> 00:01:25.610
Cover the walls of your house with a snowflake
gossamer.

00:01:25.610 --> 00:01:26.750
Step 5.

00:01:26.750 --> 00:01:32.930
Use green garland as curtain tie-backs, draping
it on the tops of windows and across the table.

00:01:32.930 --> 00:01:34.140
Step 6.

00:01:34.140 --> 00:01:40.450
Wrap empty boxes with white paper and coordinating
color ribbons and place them around your house.

00:01:40.450 --> 00:01:41.500
Step 7.

00:01:41.500 --> 00:01:45.530
Place a cutout snowman by the door of your
house to greet your guests and welcome them

00:01:45.530 --> 00:01:47.780
into your winter wonderland.

